So the robot couldn’t follow the requested path. The fix was to start over in steps. First check if the ks, kv, ka values allow controlling the speed. Run a test where you simply try to drive forward at a constant speed, and check that the robot indeed runs at that speed. Then try path follower/ramsete with a low maximum speed.
